,{"pid":"5ee42c54b1bdbbbdd2a8e6162d702777246dde61","tid":1018290,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T14:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a9b80d442afbf4af776dd56b15d44049428e6d","tid":1018290,"uid":225357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac13d01e22585d3f7ca222828fa39d5cf7b6cd84","tid":1018290,"uid":225357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43a8183796572f25dde7537cf710ea9463a2a923","tid":1018290,"uid":218082,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"人地一早都話自己係一個退出咗政壇嘅過氣廢老,係熱狗同泛民成日死唔斷氣狙擊驚佢復出咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇咗黃毓民呢班友真係隨時冇埋生存意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4fea1d05fad047ca996282e50a0e57c3a8be10","tid":1018290,"uid":128261,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43a8183796572f25dde7537cf710ea9463a2a923","tid":1018290,"uid":218082,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"人地一早都話自己係一個退出咗政壇嘅過氣廢老,係熱狗同泛民成日死唔斷氣狙擊驚佢復出咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇咗黃毓民呢班友真係隨時冇埋生存意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:56:05.000Z","msg":"退出咗政壇嘅過氣廢老？佢同佢啲毓粉例如仇思達仲成日鬧泛民同熱狗wor，連搞個show都係主力鬧人，黃毓民自己一樣死唔斷氣者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb13ffdc2bcde3057a2896c635ed2b54cb05d7c","tid":1018290,"uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T19:04:20.000Z","msg":"//美其名為「議會抗爭」。所以youtube 片段，只是重複八年來在議會的謾罵片<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">斷</span></strong></span>//<br />\n字都未識學咩人寫文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cec7c43d5d74f0ea86f47c2d3251e7a638bbf4b","tid":1018290,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T19:06:21.000Z","msg":"都係牙達個笑話show好睇啲<br />\n<br />\n笑撚到爆腸   入左急症"}]}